OL,5,Carson
OL,7,FResidents in a spa town in
OL,8,FWorcestershire say they are
OL,9,F"desperate" to save an historic Grade
OL,10,FII listed hotel that was damaged in a
OL,11,Fsuspected arson attack earlier this
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FThe Raven hotel, located in Droitwich
OL,15,FSpa town centre, dates back 500 years
OL,16,Fbut has been left derelict since it
OL,17,Fclosed its doors in 2010.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
