OL,5,Carson
OL,7,FThe fire in August caused significant
OL,8,Fstructural damage to the building and
OL,9,Fit now needs scaffolding to keep it
OL,10,Ffrom falling down.
OL,12,FThe developer, Inroka Limited, told
OL,13,FITV News Central it would cost around
OL,14,F#1.4 million to restore the building.
OL,16,FNow, a group of residents have formed
OL,17,Fthe Raven Heartbeat Group and are
OL,18,Fplanning to buy the hotel.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
