OL,7,FNicky Maguire, founder of the Raven
OL,8,FHeartbeat Group, said she thinks it's
OL,9,Fmore important now than ever to save
OL,10,Fthe hotel.
OL,12,FShe said: "What's there at the moment
OL,13,Fwe need to preserve and save, and it's
OL,14,Fnow about getting that done as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible.
OL,17,F"Bits of tiles and mortar are falling
OL,18,Fall the time, which we are very
OL,19,Fworried about.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
