OL,4,C500-year-old hotel after suspected
OL,5,Carson
OL,7,F"The building is in a very bad
OL,8,Fcondition, we would like to put a
OL,9,Fscaffold enclosure over the roof of
OL,10,Fthe listed section so it can be
OL,11,Fprotected from the harsh weather over
OL,12,Fwinter."
OL,14,FShe also says the hotel means a lot to
OL,15,Fthe town, adding: "Everyone would
OL,16,Fstill talk about the Raven like it was
OL,17,Fstill in use, like they still worked
OL,18,Fthere or were attending family
OL,19,Fcelebrations, so it's very upsetting.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
