OL,3,CResidents determined to save iconic
OL,4,C500-year-old hotel after suspected
OL,5,Carson
OL,7,F"It doesn't appear that the owner has
OL,8,Fmuch interest in it, and we would like
OL,9,Fto take on that opportunity and be
OL,10,Fvery invested and interested in it and
OL,11,Fmake sure that we don't lose any more
OL,12,Fof the building."
OL,14,FThe Raven Heartbeat group want to
OL,15,Frestore the listed section of the
OL,16,Fhotel, turning it into a shared
OL,17,Fcommunity space for people to use.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
