OL,7,FThey have recently become a community
OL,8,Finterest company, which they say will
OL,9,Fhelp them to attract funding from
OL,10,Fheritage charities.
OL,12,FPaul White is another member of the
OL,13,Fgroup and he owns five businesses at
OL,14,Fthe back of the hotel.
OL,16,FHe said: "The hotel is right on the
OL,17,Fdoorstep, I can't bear the thought of
OL,18,Fthe hotel being left to fall down.
OL,19,FSome of the people were in tears about
OL,20,Fthe condition of the hotel at the
OL,21,Ffirst meeting.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
