OL,5,Carson
OL,7,F"We are making good progress now as a
OL,8,Fgroup, which I am positive about, and
OL,9,Fwe are passionate about getting this
OL,10,Fdone.
OL,12,F"The hotel is currently an eyesore
OL,13,Fbecause it's covered in scaffolding
OL,14,Fand the fire has closed the street
OL,15,Fwhich has meant we have lost that part
OL,16,Fof the town."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
