OL,7,FInroka Limited took on the project
OL,8,Ffour years ago to build houses and was
OL,9,Fgranted planning permission in
OL,10,FNovember 2024 by Wychavon District
OL,11,FCouncil, however construction has not
OL,12,Fyet begun.
OL,14,FRajinder Singh, from Inroka, said:
OL,15,F"The cost of dealing with the asbestos
OL,16,Fand the damp now is around 1.4 million.
OL,18,F"We are here through this process and
OL,19,Fhaven't abandoned the project despite
OL,20,Fit's difficulties.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
