OL,4,C500-year-old hotel after suspected
OL,5,Carson
OL,7,F"If the group are genuine about being
OL,8,Fable to deliver this project then I am
OL,9,Fhere and they are welcome to work with
OL,10,Fme but there are conditions around the
OL,11,Fdemolition and planning that they have
OL,12,Fto satisfy."
OL,14,FDaniel Birch, local councillor at
OL,15,FWychavon District Council, told ITV
OL,16,FNews Central that he believes the
OL,17,Fbuilding is "not a lost cause".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
