OL,7,FCllr Birch said: "I think the group is
OL,8,Fbrilliant, it's an incredibly
OL,9,Fimportant cause, and Droitwich has a
OL,10,Fhistory of saving community assets. I
OL,11,Fthink it's the community, not the
OL,12,Fcouncil, that ultimately saves these
OL,13,Fsites.
OL,15,F"I am happy to be part of the group,
OL,16,Fas someone who had grandparents and
OL,17,Fparents who had receptions there, I
OL,18,Fwant to see it saved both as a
OL,19,Fresident and a councillor.
