OL,7,F"There is funding available, and the
OL,8,Fcouncil has their reserves and the
OL,9,Fgroup can earn money through
OL,10,Ffundraisers so there is money
OL,11,Favailable."
OL,13,FThe police investigation into the fire
OL,14,Fis still ongoing, and West Mercia
OL,15,FPolice say two teenage girls remain on
OL,16,Fbail on suspicion of arson.
